snippet.title: Cart Life - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the announcement trailer for upcoming retail simulation game, Cart Life. Focusing on three everyday people trying to make it as street vendors, Cart Life encourages us to guide Andrus, Melanie, and Vinny as they sell items, secure trading permits, and decide where to set up their businesses. Balance your budget and make important decisions as you grow and shape each new venture. 

Publisher AdHoc Studio and developer Richard Hofmeier plan to release Cart Life on PC via Steam sometime in 2023. The game is available to wishlist on Steam now.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
